oo was revived as a given name in its own right in the first half of the 20th century. It has to some extent been influenced by the independently formed combination <i>Jo Anne</i>."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Jehanne de DOMART was born about 1096, in Domart-en-Ponthieu, Somme, Picardie, France, her father, Gauthier Wauthier de Domart III, was 39 and her mother, Anne de BEAUMETZ, was 26. She married Charles de Beauval in 1115. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died about 1138, in Beauval, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France, at the age of 44."},"et":{"ABT 1096–ABT 1138":"umbes 1096–umbes 1138","1088–1142":"1088–1142","1096–1138":"1096–1138","1102–1158":"1102–1158","1084–1135":"1084–1135","1084–Male":"1084–Surnud","1118–1174":"1118–1174","1058–1119":"1058–1119","1072–1134":"1072–1134","1088":"1088","1142":"1142","ABT 1138":"umbes 1138","1174":"1174","1096":"1096","1084":"1084","1072":"1072","1118":"1118","ABT 1096":"umbes 1096","1138":"1138","1115":"1115","1158":"1158","1135":"1135","1058":"1058","1102":"1102","ABT 1134":"umbes 1134","1134":"1134","1119":"1119","Domart-en-Ponthieu,80620,Somme,Picardie,FRANCE,":"Domart-en-Ponthieu, Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Domart-en-Ponthieu, 80241, Somme, Picardie, France":"Domart-en-Ponthieu, Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Beauval,80630,Somme,Hauts-de-France,FRANCE,":"Beauval, Somme, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"ABT 1096–ABT 1138":"noin 1096–noin 1138","1088–1142":"1088–1142","1096–1138":"1096–1138","1102–1158":"1102–1158","1084–1135":"1084–1135","1084–Male":"1084–Kuollut","1118–1174":"1118–1174","1058–1119":"1058–1119","1072–1134":"1072–1134","1088":"1088","1142":"1142","ABT 1138":"noin 1138","1174":"1174","1096":"1096","1084":"1084","1072":"1072","1118":"1118","ABT 1096":"noin 1096","1138":"1138","1115":"1115","1158":"1158","1135":"1135","1058":"1058","1102":"1102","ABT 1134":"noin 1134","1134":"1134","1119":"1119","Domart-en-Ponthieu,80620,Somme,Picardie,FRANCE,":"Domart-en-Ponthieu, Somme, Picardie, Ranska","Do